data.description: ***NEW PRICE $315,000 , Seller will also contribute up to $5,000 in buyers closing cost or toward rate buy down with acceptable offer!***Welcome to this charming corner lot home located in the desirable Spring Lake at Bluebonnet Highlands Subdivision. Built in 1995, this beautifully maintained residence offers both comfort and style. The detached garage gives you a cottage like style, conveniently connected to the main house though a breeze way. As you step inside this home you are met with lots of natural light while charmed with the original hardwood floors. This home, thoughtfully designed, features a split floor plan including a formal dining room and breakfast nook which both open up to the living area. The primary suite is your personal oasis providing private access/views to the community lake . The primary suite provides separate walk-in closets, double vanities in the bath, including a separate whirlpool jetted tub, separate shower, with plenty of space and storage to offer. Both secondary rooms have ample space inside while having their own large walk in closets. The Subdivision offers residents access to a community pool, playground, recreational field for sports, tennis court , plus a community clubhouse ! Location is everything here with swift access to I-10 and I-12, commuting becomes a breeze, LSU, the Mall of Louisiana, restaurants, and more ensure that you're never far from entertainment, education, and everyday necessities. Schedule your private showing today !
